<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />Moses and Aaron were among his priests,</para>

<para style="q1">and Samuel was among those who prayed to him.</para>

<para style="q1">They prayed to Yahweh, and he answered them.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />He spoke to them from the pillar of cloud.</para>

<para style="q1">They kept his solemn commands</para>

<para style="q1">and the statutes that he gave them.</para>
